{"tid":2050509,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【撐學生交學費】累積14周籌762萬 望讀者繼續施援手助被經濟封鎖學生","createTime":"2020-06-04T07:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T01:33:00.000Z","uid":34410,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9d8a4926165173a4b2fe07da3c2c62fcc8ccda","tid":2050509,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:31:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200603/7BHOXDK3HRINSMP7IUJF3FDTOA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200603%2F7BHOXDK3HRINSMP7IUJF3FDTOA%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY54O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=cc946c53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200603%2F7BHOXDK3HRINSMP7IUJF3FDTOA%2F&h=4f0965d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200603/7BHOXDK3HRINSMP7IUJF3FDTOA/</a><br />\n<br />\n自去年6月開始，逆權運動觸發不少家庭問題個案，受影響的大部份是一班前線大學生與大專院校學生，他們被逐出家門，一餐未能溫飽外，甚至被經濟封鎖而無法交學費繼續過校園生活。加上近月武漢肺炎肆虐，父母收入同時受到影響而陷入家庭財政困局。「蘋果日報慈善基金」（簡稱「蘋果基金」）成立「撐學生專戶」（專戶編號：S0036），截至昨日（5月31日）捐款已有逾762萬，目前正協助10多名學生，並陸續收到其他學生申請，多謝各位熱心讀者支持。有心人捐款方法<br />\n<br />\n學生申請資格及方法<br />\n今次「蘋果日報慈善基金」（簡稱「蘋果基金」）成立「撐學生專戶」（專戶編號：S0036），繼續呼籲有心人、同路人去資助這班有家歸不得，同時有經濟困難的學生渡過難關。自1995年已成立的「蘋果基金」，為稅務局認可慈善機構，多年來一直致力幫助社會上有困難個案，現呼籲同路人、有心人去資助這班前線學生。至於欲申請此計劃希望受惠的學生，歡迎主動聯絡我們。<br />\n<br />\n學生申請資格：因反送中運動引發家庭問題，而無法繳交相關學習費用（例如學費、院校宿舍費用等）的就讀本港大專院校的大專生及大學生。「撐學生專戶」申請資格及詳細資料連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2HlIx1b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HlIx1b&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY54O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=3092a4fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2HlIx1b</a><br />\n<br />\n學生申請方法：WhatsApp&amp;Telegram：9862 7828 電郵： charity@adfund.org.hk 電話：2990 8688<br />\n有心人捐款方法（專戶編號：S0036）<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【撐學生】程式員孖寶變抗爭後勤 買校服買書畀學費<br />\n<br />\n&ndash; 以PPS或信用卡作網上捐款<br />\n&ndash; 銀行存款：<br />\n滙豐銀行：580-198836-001<br />\n恒生銀行：368-006565-001<br />\n東亞銀行（往來戶口）：015-514-68-01678-5<br />\n註：請於入數紙／支票背面寫上S0036專戶編號，然後電郵／傳真／WhatsApp訊息／郵寄予本基金。<br />\n&ndash; 現金捐款（OK便利店）（向店員表示捐款至「蘋果基金」）<br />\n&ndash; 填妥捐款表格透過VISA、Mastercard或AE信用卡捐款<br />\n學生申請資格及方法<br />\n<br />\n「撐學生專戶」專戶編號：S0036<br />\n「撐學生專戶」申請資料連結<br />\n電話：2990 8688<br />\n傳真：2307 6307<br />\n電郵:charity@adfund.org.hk<br />\nWhatsApp&amp;Telegram：9862 7828<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想捐612 可以試下捐蘋果慈善基金撐學生專戶 仲可以退稅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e770979fe9fa1f9813e35146b38e238ca9e4b333","tid":2050509,"uid":86643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92778fe8b633018d3d789095798292401389b9eb","tid":2050509,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43753f14a4872facb5221539bae9bad5e1e44290","tid":2050509,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6cae8e5d2f58b4cd023d2dca69515926f43817e","tid":2050509,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:13:49.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"8e24715f40394f88f659cb76e0dc17b855b832f3","tid":2050509,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:19:22.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 七百幾萬其實都唔係好多"},{"pid":"9fb66ccb4c858fbd2ff4d152b7b9381eaba84949","tid":2050509,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce8975993480c2ecb9f76ce241be8ec9b1d1556","tid":2050509,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":